manifest_analysis.title: Launch Mode of Activity (com.coinburp.mobile.MainActivity) is not standard.
manifest_analysis.desc: An Activity should not be having the launch mode attribute set to "singleTask/singleInstance" as it becomes root Activity and it is possible for other applications to read the contents of the calling Intent. So it is required to use the "standard" launch mode attribute when sensitive information is included in an Intent.
manifest_analysis.name: Launch Mode of Activity is not standard.

playstore_details.description:
INTRODUCING OUR NEW BETA APP
We’ve added to the CoinBurp family by launching our very own iOS and Android applications, making our services more accessible than ever before.

COINBURP IS EASY, INSTANT AND HAS NO DEPOSIT OR TRADE FEES
Register in minutes, deposit instantly and make a trade with our super-easy trading experience.

More reasons to choose us:

★ User cryptocurrency is insured up to £100 Million
★ We’re partnered with FCA-regulated banks
★ Our products and services are rated “Excellent” on Trustpilot

WE ACCEPT BRITISH POUND & EURO
Deposit by bank transfer; British Pound (GBP) with UK FPS and Euro (EUR) with SEPA.

NOW LISTING 5 TRADABLE CRYPTOS
Deposit Bitcoin (BTC), Bitcoin Cash (BCH), Ethereum (ETH), Litecoin (LTC) and Ripple (XRP) by wallet transfer.

-

WHO ARE COINBURP?

CoinBurp is a family of products and services that allow people to buy, store and sell cryptocurrencies, like Bitcoin (BTC), Bitcoin Cash (BCH), Ethereum (ETH), Litecoin (LTC) and Ripple (XRP), via the super-easy CoinBurp beta app and website; www.coinburp.com.

With one of the quickest and easiest registration processes, instant British Pound (GBP) deposits and withdrawals, as well as Euro (EUR) support and some of the lowest fees on the market, CoinBurp is now one of the fastest growing cryptocurrency trading platforms in the UK.

-

Here are the main features of the CoinBurp beta app:

FAST-TRACK ON-BOARDING
Get trading in no longer than 15 minutes with our fast-track registration and verification process, experienced entirely in-house.

INSTANT DEPOSITS
Deposit cryptocurrency from an external wallet and British Pound (GBP) or Euro (EUR) by bank transfer. Receive British Pound (GBP) instantly and Euro (EUR) within the same day.

AUTOMATED WITHDRAWALS
Withdraw instantly with our automated withdrawals system, which automatically processes withdrawal requests 24/7, 365 days a year.

SUPER-EASY TRADING
We’ve transformed the traditional trading experience into 3 simple steps to make buying and selling our listed currencies super-easy.

BANK-GRADE SECURITY
We safeguard user funds, transaction data and personal details in bank-grade encrypted storage, and protect user accounts with mandatory 2FA.

OUTSTANDING SUPPORT
We’re dedicated to providing a personable customer service and an outstanding level of support that is surpassing industry standards.

LISTED CRYPTOCURRENCIES
Bitcoin (BTC), Bitcoin Cash (BCH), Ethereum (ETH), Litecoin (LTC), Ripple (XRP).

-

CoinBurp is a registered trademark and a private limited company incorporated and registered under the laws of England and Wales with company number 11439823 and registered office address at 1 Ropemaker St, London, United Kingdom, EC2Y 9AW.

Enumis Limited is CoinBurp's GBP banking partner; authorised and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority as an Electronic Money Institution (FRN 900028) and authorised and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority for Consumer Credit (FRN 724110). We provide EUR services via BCB Payments Ltd - regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority, no. 807377.

CoinBurp does not provide advice to the users of its service. Please seek your own legal, tax or investment advice as you deem appropriate.
